
Project Structure Overview:

weather_app.py (Main - GUI)
├── imports weather_api.py
├── reads .env
└── shows GUI window

streamlit_weather_app.py (Main - Web)
├── imports weather_api.py
├── reads .env
└── launches web app

weather_api.py (Helper)
├── handles API requests
├── processes weather/forecast data
└── provides sample data
